		<div id="comment_body_64116837"><p>1) It's a new story, to take it with a pound of salt.<br>2) This "job" isn't much like yours.  Others being replaced are.  The point of this story is to reduce the disapproval of those other jobs being automated.<br>3) Automating jobs is good, as long as you care for those who are injured in the process.  But we prefer to avoid that expense.</p></div>
	</div>

